             .max(Comparator.comparing(FileDetails::getUploadedDate))
             .get();
```
Note `max` returns an `Optional&lt;FileDetails&gt;`.  I presume that at least one file would be there so it was safe to use `get` to retrieve it from the Optional.  You can also do the following:
```
