Your update target should invoke ivy:resolve task after ivy:settings.

    &lt;target name=&quot;update&quot; depends=&quot;init-ivy&quot; description=&quot;Download project dependencies&quot;&gt;
      &lt;ivy:settings file=&quot;ivysettings.xml&quot; /&gt;
